== Project Proposal

I am studying mechanical engineering with an interest in aerospace. For my final
project, I wanted to choose a project that combined my interests in aircraft and
embedded systems. So I have chosen to build a functional flight emulator that
brings together physical analog gauges, a digital display, and a computer
dashboard to recreate what it's like to monitor aircraft instruments in
real-time. The idea is to take the complexity of an actual cockpit and make it
tangible and interactive.


My proposal is to design and build a flight simulation system using
Arduino-based microcontrollers, featuring motorized analog gauges that respond
to real-time flight parameters. The system will be integrated with a digital
display and a software dashboard for visualization, control, and data logging,
creating a cohesive hardware-software platform that emulates aircraft
instrumentation.

